##  Hardware Log

* An ESP32 project that shows the verse headings for each day's lectionary Readings according to the USCCB. *

Started as a personal project to retry my hand at embedded hardware and software.
All Readings are taken from USCCB.com

- Micro Controller
	- Model: **Inland ESP32 Core Board
	- Compiler: **Arduino IDE
	- Pinout: #Here
- Stepper Motor
	- Model: **28BYJ-48**
	- Controller Board: **Inland UN2003
	- SW Library: **`<Stepper.h>
- 1.3 Inch OLED
	- Model: **Inland OLED Graphic Display
	- Width: **128px
	- Height: **64px
	- SW Library: **`<U8g2lib.h>
- Rotary Encoder Switch
	- Model: **Inland
	- Misc part


